Are you saying that you're abandoning me?

816
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:20,070
Is it because no one is buying my book?

817
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:22,510
Is that why you're abandoning me as well?

818
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:28,190
I don't know how to
explain it to you right now,

819
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:29,470
but,

820
00:40:30,350 --> 00:40:31,870
Suo Heng, I'm sorry.

821
00:40:32,310 --> 00:40:33,750
I didn't expect you

822
00:40:33,750 --> 00:40:34,990
to deviate from your original style

823
00:40:34,990 --> 00:40:36,550
after you did your research

824
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:38,870
on how to write better.

825
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,470
Maybe it's my fault.

826
00:40:42,990 --> 00:40:43,470
Sis Yao Yao,

827
00:40:43,470 --> 00:40:45,750
can you please trust me one last time?

828
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:48,390
Please trust me one last time, okay?

829
00:40:52,590 --> 00:40:53,430
Fine.

830
00:40:54,710 --> 00:40:56,070
I understand now.

831
00:40:57,190 --> 00:40:59,270
Thank you for caring for me
all these years.

832
00:41:00,550 --> 00:41:02,590
From now on,
we'll be on our separate ways.

833
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:03,750
We are even now.

834
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:07,790
I was so naive that I thought

835
00:41:09,350 --> 00:41:11,660
the dreams you told me before
were your true dreams.

836
00:41:15,350 --> 00:41:16,870
Just throw away the keys.

837
00:41:25,270 --> 00:41:26,390
Chief Editor Yu,

838
00:41:26,620 --> 00:41:28,940
why didn't you tell her that...

839
00:41:29,910 --> 00:41:31,110
Because

840
00:41:31,110 --> 00:41:32,790
I was pregnant back then.

841
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:35,150
The doctor said

842
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:36,790
it'll be hard for the child to survive

843
00:41:36,790 --> 00:41:38,620
if I didn't rest well.

844
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:41,110
Why didn't you tell her then?

845
00:41:41,430 --> 00:41:43,030
Even if I had told her,
that wouldn't have changed anything.

846
00:41:45,030 --> 00:41:47,150
Even if I had told tell her that

847
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:48,790
I didn't want to give up on her,

848
00:41:50,620 --> 00:41:53,070
what would have that changed?

849
00:41:53,070 --> 00:41:55,230
It won't change anything.

850
00:41:57,790 --> 00:41:59,470
I'm sorry, Chief Editor Yu.

851
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,270
Stop it.

852
00:42:01,990 --> 00:42:04,070
You're not the one
who should apologize here.

853
00:42:07,270 --> 00:42:08,350
Sorry for that.

854
00:42:08,790 --> 00:42:10,270
I have things to attend to.
I'll leave now.

855
00:42:17,670 --> 00:42:18,390
Chu Li,

856
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:20,070
let's go.

857
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:29,430
It's fine as long as she's alive.

858
00:42:29,870 --> 00:42:31,350
If you want her to pull herself together,

859
00:42:31,350 --> 00:42:32,910
you'll have plenty of time to do so
in the future.

860
00:42:36,310 --> 00:42:38,390
I watched Ms Suo Heng

861
00:42:38,910 --> 00:42:40,790
as she couldn't say anything

862
00:42:40,790 --> 00:42:42,830
or do anything about her circumstances.

863
00:42:43,350 --> 00:42:45,180
She worked so hard,

864
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:48,380
even the ink of her keyboard has faded.

865
00:42:49,910 --> 00:42:51,590
In this world,

866
00:42:52,780 --> 00:42:54,310
there are many helpless situations.

867
00:42:54,470 --> 00:42:56,070
Your effort might not be repaid.

868
00:42:56,470 --> 00:42:57,910
But, if you can move on bravely

869
00:42:57,910 --> 00:42:59,550
even after realizing the truth,

870
00:43:00,950 --> 00:43:01,830
these difficulties you've faced

871
00:43:01,830 --> 00:43:03,350
won't become ordeals to you.

872
00:43:03,350 --> 00:43:05,270
They'll become a meaningful experience

873
00:43:05,270 --> 00:43:06,950
to you.

874
00:43:13,190 --> 00:43:14,670
Sir, I'm sorry.

875
00:43:14,670 --> 00:43:17,750
Did I mention your sad past by accident?

876
00:43:20,150 --> 00:43:21,830
I'm different from you.

877
00:43:21,830 --> 00:43:23,260
I'm a genius.

878
00:43:23,260 --> 00:43:24,870
Geniuses don't need to put in effort.

879
00:43:25,950 --> 00:43:29,230
Your confidence is what I like about you.

880
00:43:30,390 --> 00:43:31,470
Let's go.
